,{"pid":"442893e919be0dbffc3231484abb3176705435c4","tid":85981,"uid":35760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:27:38.000Z","msg":"爆手足口點解係柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be40931d2319d434f1041f595f9adbf66426244","tid":85981,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:43:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆手足口點解係柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n手足口病一種兒童傳染病，又名發疹性水皰性口腔炎。<span style=\"color: red;\">多發生於5歲以下兒童</span>，可引起手、足、口腔等部位的皰疹，少數患兒可引起心肌炎、肺水腫、無菌性腦膜腦炎等併發症。有些重症患兒如果病情發展快，導致死亡。該病以手、足和口腔粘膜皰疹或破潰後形成潰瘍為主要臨床症狀。手足口病是由腸道病毒引起的傳染病，引發手足口病的腸道病毒有20多種（型），其中以柯薩奇病毒A16型（Cox A16）和腸道病毒71型（EV71）最為常見[1][2]。1957年新西蘭首次報道該病，1959年提出手足口病命名[2]。<br />\n<br />\n細佬仔先患手足口病，咁大個都咁唔衛生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613033a7e2e7ad4b03df625e93c5b467d845a0bc","tid":85981,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d56e14bfcfe1b55ce417248c97442e58f5c6c1","tid":85981,"uid":10625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"然後 HKU jj 繼續無視 hall cult 問題，講一句「唔住 hall 咪得囉」就算...... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5feb7b7e55ce9cc2ad31db1c2856afdeb5a09c03","tid":85981,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後 HKU jj 繼續無視 hall cult 問題，講一句「唔住 hall 咪得囉」就算...... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇hall culture住hall黎把撚啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0f55107b446cb8edfc9fa1f74a4e9bc4e4c01f","tid":85981,"uid":4745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後 HKU jj 繼續無視 hall cu